enter for comparative studies in race & ethnicity which offers a diverse array of courses on race and ethnicity social stratification and language and cultural theory across the social sciences and humanities academics apply now master's programs doctoral programs undergraduate programs courses stanford academic calendar master's handbook doctoral handbook about ships the doctoral programs in ships combine two kinds of approaches to research in education one approach is disciplinary in which we prepare students to study education issues from one of a wide array of disciplinary perspectives we call this approach humanities and social sciences in education hss the other approach is issue based in which we focus on major issue domains in education that are of particular salience to educational policy we call this approach issue domains in education ide these issue domains include read more stanford university school of education 485 lasuen mall stanford ca 94305 3096 tel 650 723 2109 copyright 2012 stanford university all rights reserved terms of use copyright complaints site map contact us helpsu suse it axess academic calendar stanford bulletin office of the registrar edmail stanfordwho stanfordyou login connect with us on facebook connect with us on twitter connect with us on youtube connect with us on flickr make a gift now
